It sounds like you want a SlewRateLimiter   we use one in our Teleop driving command.

We declare private SlewRateLimiter xLimiter = new SlewRateLimiter(3); This creates a limiter that allows for 3 units change per second.   In this case 1 unit will be 100% or 1. Meaning it can reach 100% in 1/3 of a second.

it is used in code like xTranslation = -xLimiter.calculate(modifyAxis(m_gamepad.getLeftY()));
